%section.section
  %h1 Your References

  %p Talking to people who have known you over a period of time helps us get a more complete understanding of you as a future foster carer.

  %div.box.info
    %h2 Your references should be a mixture of:
    %ul.default
      %li 1-2 family members
      %li Ex-colleagues
      %li Neighbours
      %li Friends

  %section.actions
    = link_to t('continue'), new_application_referee_path(application_id: application.code, step: :name), class: "button confirm"
    .other_actions
      = link_to :back, class: "back" do
        =fa_icon "caret-left"
        =t('back')
